highlights.text: Olivia Dean has the most spots on Viral Songs Philippines. “Man I Need” is the highest at #5.
“Stay with Me” by Huh Gak is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Philippines at #8.
“About You” by The 1975 has been on Viral Songs Philippines the longest, at 302 days straight.
“Innocence” by Hildir Svensson and Six Dior is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Philippines, up 13 spots at #49.
